statements: SELECT * FROM SustainableFashionEvents;
SELECT event_name, event_date, event_location FROM SustainableFashionEvents;
SELECT event_name, organizer_name FROM SustainableFashionEvents WHERE event_date = '2022-05-15';
SELECT event_name, event_location FROM SustainableFashionEvents WHERE organizer_name = 'ABC Events';
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_date FROM SustainableFashionEvents ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM SustainableFashionEvents WHERE event_location = 'New York' ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT event_name, event_location, organizer_name FROM SustainableFashionEvents WHERE event_location = 'Paris' ORDER BY event_date ASC;
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_location FROM SustainableFashionEvents WHERE organizer_name = 'Fashion Forward Events' ORDER BY event_location ASC, event_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM SustainableFashionEvents WHERE event_date BETWEEN '2022-07-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY event_date ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_events, event_location FROM SustainableFashionEvents GROUP BY event_location HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY total_events DESC, event_location ASC;
